    <briefdescription>
<para>Enumeration for specifying what the Input Method &quot;action&quot; button functionality is set to. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The &apos;Action&apos; button is traditionally the [RETURN] or [DONE] button. Not all these actions are supported by all systems. Setting a custom label will still require one of these actions to be set. @SINCE_1_3.20 </para>
